      "data": {
        "identity": {
          "graphId": "tutorial-start-here"
        },
        "markdown": "## First path\n\n1. If you need to open an LLM and complete the Twilite handshake, use **Bootstrap Your LLM**.\n2. If you want to understand the graph model itself, go to **Basic Primitives**.\n3. If you want to learn the application surface, go to **Interface Tutorial**.\n4. If you want broader context about the product and philosophy, open **About Twilite**.\n\nThis graph should orient you, not trap you.",
        "_placement": {
          "version": 1,
          "state": "auto-placed",
          "source": "layout",
          "updatedAt": 1781399661723,
          "reason": "auto-layout"
        }
      }
    },
